                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1080700150" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1080700150">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/140056369/">贺大侠</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">阔以说是微言大义，除了讲统治者治家那一块，剩下的无论是修身，齐家都有借鉴意义。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

